dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: Colega superior! A question I do have!

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: Go on.

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: I have heard tell that WARP trains take roundabout paths across the Outskirts so as to prevent crashes during high-speed travel; are these tales correct?

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: They are not.

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: I—I see… Permit me another! Is it of verity that first-class passengers are provided with an apéritif from the “vacuum cellar” in 17-dimensional warp space?

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: They are not.

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: Ahem… W-Well, I can say I had a feeling that such frivolous chronicles would be untrue! Then, about our fellow agents…

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: Miss Don Quixote was your name, correct?

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: Verily so!

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: …Why don’t you take a seat. You’ll be able to see the train with your own eyes in no time.

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: WHAT HO!!!!!! I—I shall do as such!
Little did this child know…
There was a reason her senior colleague cut short her questioning spree.
There was a reason her answers were so short and simple.
After that, it wasn’t long until the child learned the real truth.

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: …I won’t stop you from having fantasies, Miss Don Quixote.

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: This… This is…

dataList.title: W Corp. Cleanup Agent
dataList.content: Just please keep in mind that reality may not quite align with them.
Brought face-to-face with what lie within the newly-arrived train, the child sat in place, her face filled with disconcertment and disgust.
Of course, anyone would react like that.
Those carriages… Learning the truth behind them does that.
